text: Katalin Müller-Száll (born 13 September 1943) is a Hungarian gymnast. She competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics, the 1964 Summer Olympics and the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
